&lt;p>Speed Painting: Keyes Beholding–SotN Grim Reaper&lt;/p>
&lt;p>As a fun exercise I decided to find a screen shot of one of the greatest 2d side scrolling games ever made, Castlevania SotN.  Eventually I’d like to create an entire HD remix of the screen shot as a fun wallpaper background.  For now, I’m going to try and go through piece by piece as a study.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>